column5: Rainbows are growing nicely, check out the size difference in these tanks, January should bring Weighing & Sorting to get them ready to be fin clipped, keep your ears open for the LHFC looking for volunteers again if your interested. Tight Lines SBK Rainbow Trout Hatchery Video
